學生會：至少9同學被捕<br />\n<br />\n截至昨午6時，中大學生會稱至少9名同學被捕，中大校方證實有學生被捕，對事件表示關注，會按需要提供可行協助；浸大學生會了解到至少1名同學被捕，已獲釋，並指約6名同學曾被搜身；浸大校方稱沒收到學生求助。理大、城大學生會回覆指有同學被搜身，沒被即時拘捕。<br />\n上一頁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190611/s00001/1560191265118/%e7%95%99%e5%ae%88%e8%80%85-%e9%bb%91%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba%e7%aa%81%e6%b9%a7%e7%8f%be-%e7%a8%b1%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%8b%e7%8f%ad%e8%b6%95%e4%be%86%e6%89%be%e5%a5%b3%e5%8f%8b%e3%80%8d?fbclid=IwAR1EYNEpKvDUXRTEmSCfqnTf5eTqeq100yoieJ6-5DTLGiaO9zvpk6v6Jxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190611%2Fs00001%2F1560191265118%2F%25e7%2595%2599%25e5%25ae%2588%25e8%2580%2585-%25e9%25bb%2591%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%25aa%2581%25e6%25b9%25a7%25e7%258f%25be-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%258b%25e7%258f%25ad%25e8%25b6%2595%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%2589%25be%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%258f%258b%25e3%2580%258d%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1EYNEpKvDUXRTEmSCfqnTf5eTqeq100yoieJ6-5DTLGiaO9zvpk6v6Jxg&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=bab5bc53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190611%2Fs00001%2F1560191265118%2F%25e7%2595%2599%25e5%25ae%2588%25e8%2580%2585-%25e9%25bb%2591%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%25aa%2581%25e6%25b9%25a7%25e7%258f%25be-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%258b%25e7%258f%25ad%25e8%25b6%2595%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%2589%25be%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%258f%258b%25e3%2580%258d%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1EYNEpKvDUXRTEmSCfqnTf5eTqeq100yoieJ6-5DTLGiaO9zvpk6v6Jxg&h=78a88049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190611/s00001/1560191265118/%e7%95%99%e5%ae%88%e8%80%85-%e9%bb%91%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba%e7%aa%81%e6%b9%a7%e7%8f%be-%e7%a8%b1%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%8b%e7%8f%ad%e8%b6%95%e4%be%86%e6%89%be%e5%a5%b3%e5%8f%8b%e3%80%8d?fbclid=IwAR1EYNEpKvDUXRTEmSCfqnTf5eTqeq100yoieJ6-5DTLGiaO9zvpk6v6Jxg</a>"},{"pid":"